Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have reports of crustal movement and abnormal weather all over the world!{from ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The breaking of the seal on the Legendary Aquarion is affecting the whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can't contact the Elements, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only option is sending the machines we have left to Altair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how? The Dimension Gate is closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open a hole through the dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know last time was an accident, and Shrade was there to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it, Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't, all the holes I've ever dug were pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy W. Hol...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take a risk using your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare oppose me, Wings of the Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to secure the true Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid the core units! Disable their weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think that'll work, Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of the Wings of the Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is enough power to wipe out a Gnis platoon all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send it back at you amplified!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's firing it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just reverse it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His power of reversal is canceling out my counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo! You can't have my wench, even over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you, Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you care about that Rare Igura so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my smelly wench! Only mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Izumo, I'll fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Abductor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Mix?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Izumo is Altair's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, be safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been a while since it was just us guys in a Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to reach the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this done! With a manly Brutal Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how we Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing a hot-blooded Warrior's Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Gepard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what your body's turned into!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always come for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what I used to say, Mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holes are dug to bring the world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hole's to bring us to that world you're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll open another great big hole into your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big enough to bury myself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The artificial Dimension Gate has formed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get 'em, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard someone calling my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! My name is Mixy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix is the pilot of that robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go reverse out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Gepard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we butted right into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Abductors and the Legendary Aquarion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are the pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cayenne! Is that you, Cayenne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono! What are you doing with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mix's machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two Abductors are trying to get Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Amata and Shrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade... is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He played out his final song in the dimensional rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare oppose Sir Izumo as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong, Mix! I'm only here to take you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me back where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember, Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Andy W. Hol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see, Kagura? Don't you care about Altair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This planet can go to hell. I just want my smelly wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight the whole world before I give her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix! Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All for a single Igura, a single woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where that voice is calling me from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The planet. The land. The life sleeping within.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All are about to awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebirth of the Wings of the Sun was a double-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it divide the world, or reunite it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{cm}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to me, Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Augmentation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to keep this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this for as long as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make the holes, and Mix'll fill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we came to know each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he keep doing the same pointless move?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why does it feel so familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, I've been waiting so long to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:11:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for that now! After you left me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how I've felt all these years?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after all this time, you call me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask you to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why I had to leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father isn't an Earthling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Izumo Kamurogi, the commander of Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot afford to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:12:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must put an end to the curse of Eve! The Rare Igura's tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father came to Earth on a mission to find a \Nwoman who could withstand interdimensional travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He arrived back when I was an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My machine malfunctioned and I crashed on Vega. She saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't take me long to realize Alicia was the Rare Igura we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took even less time for us to fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in no position to judge Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost betrayed Altair once myself, for a single woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:14:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept her a secret from command, and we returned to Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't keep it from Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came back some years later. By then, I had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when he told me about the curse of Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? We don't know what will happen to a Rare Igura there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it'll help you, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to decide whether I should take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:15:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I was more worried that you would be in danger on a strange, unknown world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought we would be apart for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's just an excuse. I abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to help save my love's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all for the man I loved, the things I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've resented you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hate myself from back then, when all I could do was watch you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were brave enough to go after your love. I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up already, Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot lose! I will not let Alicia's sacrifice go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Aquarion is fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Izumo and the other you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ianthe, created by my mother Oriza!{was this plot ever supposed to go anywhere?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's focusing all of Altair's power into the Ahura Gnis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Altair Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the power of the planet Altair itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a warning shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the true Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or I'll shoot for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KAGURA!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel the power of the Genesis Infinity Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was all your doing, Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to Alicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask you for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took your mother from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're those?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayflies.{this is the "ephemera" thing, I should assume}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only seen them once, when I was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they went extinct a long time ago when the females died off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Area 337.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's where Ianthe has had the most malfunctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Ianthe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother Earth. The goddess of the fertile land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The land that brings forth the blessing of the harvest is symbolized by a feminine figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Male and female. Positive and negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of creation is ordered along these dualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From people to lands. From worlds to the universe itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ianthe functioned by drawing energy from the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it took away the mothering power of the land as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of this was because of Ianthe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all I have ever done...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Not when we just met!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life meant something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the hope for the two worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the symbol of our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, you need to love too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love the one person more precious to you than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:24:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ed?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.88,0:24:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My destined smelly wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.05,0:24:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.28,0:24:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.83,0:24:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I want to take all of you and hold you.{mushaburitsuku hard to tl cleanly}
